      Classes in jumpingalien.model that implement Jump 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Mazub
      This class holds a (playable) alien that is able to run, duck and jump
      class  Shark
      This class builds a shark that can run and jump the movement of this shark starts orientated to the left and will move for 0.5 seconds, then one second resting that means that the shark will not move horizontally, then 0.5 seconds to the right and then again one second of rest; this movement will be repeated until the shark is dead
      class  Skullcab
      This class builds a Skullcab that can jump at constant velocity
      class  Spider
      This class builds a spider that can run and jump and with legs that can increase or decrease in amount because of collision with features and other Game Object
